5:
Sorry for the wait! Here's your
omurice... and a little spell to make it
taste even better!
9:
Hmm... At a glance, she seems to be
doing okay.
13:
Apparently, she hasn't seen Sho a
single time since the big reveal.
20:
...What? What do you mean that
wasn't you?
23:
You're Sho! You lived in Kawasaki,
close to where I lived!
27:
We were five years old! You came to
me at 4:39 pm on May 5th! I
remember it clear as day!
31:
That was during Golden Week, right?
I was at my grandpa's place
then—nowhere near Kanagawa.
34:
Plus it's not like I'm the only Sho out
there, yeah?
38: N-no, but that would mean... I...
43: Ahaha, sorry for worrying you guys.
50:
It's okay if things aren't exactly as
you remember.
53:
What matters most is the here and
now—
61:
If it's not destiny bringing us
together, then our love isn't right.
64:
I'm not allowed to be with anyone
otherwise...
73:
Sorry, ignore that. I appreciate the
concern, but like I said, it's fine.
77:
"You're a good person—pure of heart
the whole way through. I'm only here
because you never gave up on me."
79:
"...I love you! I know we were meant
to be together!"
84:
That's how it's supposed to be—a
fateful meeting, forming into a bond
built up over time...
87: It's the right way for love to form.
91:
I'd never play around with his
feelings or make him cry!
94: That's out of the cards for you.
96:
You're that woman's daughter, after
all.
101: ...I'm so sorry... I'll clean that right up.
107: Sorry, but we came to visit again.
117:
...Even if your initial meeting wasn't
what you had in mind, can't you two
still be meant for each other?
124:
No. I have to do things right,
otherwise this love won't work.
127:
...It's my curse... for being born from
that awful woman...
142:
I might not get exactly what
romance is, but your feelings for him
are genuine, right?
145:
Sorry, I just can't leave well enough
alone in these situations.
150:
W-we've got an emergency on our
hands! A whole buncha monsters
showed up in the Kaleidoscope
outta nowhere!
152:
We need all hands on deck to beat
them back and rescue the
adventurers that're stuck in there!
155:
Sho said he'd be exploring the
Kaleidoscope today...
165:
This is no time to be standing
around. We have to go save Sho!
175:
How are you so sure he's in this
direction?
180: I put a tracker on him!
185:
Oh. That's a conversation... I'm going
to save for later...
193:
Hey, it's too early to be giving up!
You've got family, don'tcha? It's not
over until it's over!
211:
Dang... I thought I was a goner for a
sec there! I seriously owe you guys
one!
219:
Remember what we talked about?
She's still bothered by what you said
the other day.
224:
Oh. Oh! That whole "meant to be
together" thing?
234:
...I'm sorry, Sho. I should've noticed
from the beginning...
238:
It's no big deal. Who needs fate and
destiny anyway? Not me!
241:
Besides, you can like who you like. It
doesn't bother me at all.
245:
Does that mean... I can keep loving
you?
257:
Wait... I totally thought she was
gonna abandon me after all that.
261:
Aha... You really are something else,
Sho...
270:
Here. I'll give you back the key to
your place.
273:
I guess it can't hurt to ask again,
but...
277:
You're fine with being friends with
me until we get married, right?
281:
Huh? I mean, yeah, but why ask
again?
284:
...Where did you even get this key
anyway?
288: I'll do my best to treat you right...
292:
We're going to be together forever,
Sho!
297:
Hold on, answer the question, will
ya?!
